      "body": "<h2>The Perfect Everyday Tee</h2><p>We spent two years sourcing the right organic cotton and perfecting the fit. The result is a t-shirt that feels like a favorite from day one.</p><h3>Details</h3><ul><li>100% GOTS-certified organic cotton</li><li>Heavyweight 6.5oz fabric</li><li>Garment-dyed for a lived-in feel</li><li>Pre-shrunk</li><li>Side seams for a clean drape</li></ul><h3>Care</h3><p>Machine wash cold, tumble dry low. The more you wash it, the better it gets.</p>"
